This project is a fork of Telegram-Drive by Cameron Amer.
Original repository: https://github.com/caamer20/Telegram-Drive
Original license: MIT

This fork converts the original Tauri desktop application into a headless
web server suitable for self-hosted deployment.

Third-party components:
- grammers (Telegram MTProto client for Rust): https://github.com/Lonami/grammers
- Actix Web: https://actix.rs/
- React: https://react.dev/
- Vite: https://vite.dev/
- TailwindCSS: https://tailwindcss.com/

All third-party components retain their original licenses.
